cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the use of dropout for regularization in convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new pooling method, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of different pooling methods on text classification tasks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL).
